cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.NE 

The paper involves the use of deep convolutional neural networks for real-time tracking of lung deformations in radiation therapy. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves the use of information theory (cs.IT) for subspace modeling.
